<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The isLast method on Zend_Service_Amazon_SimpleDb_Page-objects checks wether the NextToken is null or not, when determining wether or not it is the last page for the query.</p>

<p>However, the Zend_Service_Amazon_SimpleDb sets the NextToken to an empty string, if there is no NextToken, so the isLast method doesn't work as intended.</p>

<p>As I see it could be fixed either in Zend_Service_Amazon_SimpleDb or Zend_Service_Amazon_SimpleDb_Page. I don't know which would be better for the framework.</p>

